title: Dow Movers: KO, INTC - Nasdaq.com
text: In early trading on Thursday, shares of Intel topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 4.3%. Year to date, Intel registers a 8.8% gain.    makeArticleAd();  And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Coca-Cola, trading down 0.1%. Coca-Cola is showing a gain of 17.6% looking at the year to date performance.      Two other components making moves today are Procter & Gamble, trading flat on the day, and Dow, trading up 3.2% on the day.        VIDEO: Dow Movers: KO, INTC
